17 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1230 of Title 36, unless there
20 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 A. For purposes of this act:
22 1. "Assignment agreement" means any instrument by which post-
23 loss benefits under an auto, or residential or commercial property
24 insurance, including, but not limited to, any right of action
